<HEADLINE> Results From Voter-Interest Poll  </HEADLINE>
   By The Associated Press
<TEXT>
<P>
	   Some results from a poll on voter interest taken for the Vanishing Voter
Project of the Joan Shorenstein Center on the Press Politics and Public Policy.
The total may exceed 100 percent because of rounding.
</P>
