picked a candidate yet?
</P>
<P>
	   --Don't currently support a candidate, 74 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --George W. Bush, 13 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --Al Gore, 6 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --John McCain, 3 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --Bill Bradley, 2 percent.
</P>
