</P>
<P>
	   --Steve Forbes, 1 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --Alan Keyes, 1 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --Support a candidate, but can't remember name, 1 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --Other, 1 percent.
</P>
