any thinking about the presidential campaign, or is this something that you
haven't been thinking about?
</P>
<P>
	   --Yes, have been thinking about campaign, 11 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   --No, haven't been thinking about campaign, 89 percent.
</P>
<P>
	   The poll of 1,012 people was taken from Dec. 28-Jan. 2 and has an error
margin of plus or minus 3 percentage points.
