</P>
<P>
	   Douglas, 55, proposed to the 30-year-old Welsh actress on New Year's Eve at
his home in Aspen, Colo.
</P>
<P>
	   "While no date has been set, they plan to wed later this year. He's now
given her a ring," said Allen Burry, Douglas' publicist.
</P>
<P>
	   Todd Adair, who represents Zeta-Jones, said the marriage proposal came with
a "big ol' diamond ring."
</P>
<P>
	   "She's ecstatic, thrilled and very, very happy," Adair said.
</P>
