	   The relationship was said to be on the rocks just last month when Zeta-Jones
opted to spend Christmas in Wales. Douglas showed up in time to join her for the
holiday.
</P>
<P>
	   The two met at the Deauville Film Festival in August 1998 and have been
dating since March 1999. They share a Sept. 25 birthday.
</P>
<P>
	   In December, the actress, who has starred in "The Mask of Zorro," "The
Haunting" and "Entrapment," said she was in no hurry to marry the star of "Fatal
Attraction" and "Basic Instinct."
</P>
<P>
	   She told Harper's Bazaar magazine then that "there are no words of
marriage." Douglas separated from his wife of 22 years, Diandra, in 1997.
</P>
