<HEADLINE> Dollar Mixed, Gold Falls  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    LONDON (AP) -- The U.S. dollar rose against the Japanese yen but fell
against other major currencies today in European trading. Gold prices fell.
</P>
