<HEADLINE> Mourners Attend Llewelyn Funeral  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   BATTLE, England (AP) -- Desmond Llewelyn, who played ``Q'' in 17 James Bond
movies, was remembered at his funeral Thursday as ``a man who loved his home and
garden.''
</P>
<P>
	   Llewelyn died Dec. 19 in a head-on car crash at the age of 85.
</P>
<P>
	   His funeral was held at the 12th-century St. Mary The Virgin Church in
Sussex, southeast England, near his home village of Bexhill.
</P>
