of him as a husband, father and grandfather -- a very loving husband, father and
grandfather.''
</P>
<P>
	   ``Desmond was a man who loved his home and his garden,'' he added.
</P>
<P>
	   Though none of the actors who have played Bond were present, the service was
attended by actress Samantha Bond, the latest Miss Moneypenny, and Colin Salmon,
who plays M's chief of staff.
</P>
<P>
	   Llewelyn's wife, Pamela, who suffers from Alzheimer's, did not attend the
funeral.
</P>
