<HEADLINE> No. 18 Arizona 71, California 58  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    TUCSON, Ariz. (AP) -- Tatum Brown scored 15 points as No. 18 Arizona
defeated California 71-58 Thursday night in a Pac-10 opener for both teams.
</P>
<P>
	   The Wildcats (12-1, 1-0) led 39-34 at the half after hitting only 35 percent
from the field but warmed up slightly to build a double-digit lead midway
through the second half.
